{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Turn-based competition is an exciting capability added in Game Center for iOS 5. Learn about the new API and user interface for turn-based play and see how it applies in a variety of popular game genres. Gain insight into managing turn-based game state and get details about how the turn is passed from player to player."}],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"content","content":[{"anchor":"overview","type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Overview"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"😱 “No Overview Available!”","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Be the hero to change that by watching the video or reading the transcript on WWDCIndex and providing notes! It’s super easy:","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"https:\/\/wwdcnotes.com\/documentation\/wwdcnotes\/contributing","type":"reference","isActive":true}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"sampleCodeDownload":{"kind":"sampleDownload","action":{"overridingTitle":"Open on WWDCIndex","identifier":"https:\/\/nonstrict.eu\/wwdcindex\/wwdc2011\/412\/","type":"reference","isActive":true}},"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"major":0,"patch":0},"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC11-412-TurnBased-Gaming-with-Game-Center","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/wwdcnotes\/wwdc11-412-turnbased-gaming-with-game-center"]}],"sections":[],"kind":"article","metadata":{"title":"Turn-Based Gaming with Game Center","role":"sampleCode","roleHeading":"WWDC11","modules":[{"name":"WWDC Notes"}]},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes","doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC11"]]},"references":{"https://nonstrict.eu/wwdcindex/wwdc2011/412/":{"url":"https:\/\/nonstrict.eu\/wwdcindex\/wwdc2011\/412\/","type":"download","checksum":null,"identifier":"https:\/\/nonstrict.eu\/wwdcindex\/wwdc2011\/412\/"},"https://wwdcnotes.com/documentation/wwdcnotes/con